.**************************************************************************
.*                                 NOBD0000                               *
.*                          Print the number of bed days                  *
.**************************************************************************
.
NOBD0000  MOVE      "11",REFERENCE
          MOVE      "NUMBER OF BED DAYS ",CURRDESC
          MOVE      "A ",CODE
          MOVE      ZERO,TOTBEDAY
.
          CALL      READ0000                * read the patient discharge and 
